        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName><sic>Chesnut</sic> Street</placeName>.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>To the <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">My Dr. Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">When you have leisure I would<lb/> like if you would answer the
                following questions</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><hi rend="underline">What were the opinions of the Jews about
                    the</hi><lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">time of Christ as to insanity</hi>?</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><hi rend="underline">If they believed the insane to be possessed
                    by</hi><lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">spirits, of what nature did they suppose the</hi><lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">spirits to be</hi>?</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">If you could refer me to any work that<lb/> I could read that would
                give the information<lb/> it would be deemed a <sic>sufficcient</sic> answer;
                and<lb/> by doing so you will oblige</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Your obe'dt Servt.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <hi rend="underline">
                    <persName role="author">P. Walker</persName>
                </hi>
            </p>
        </body>
